steam\/apps\/3117820\/extras\/6fbb1136b4d9f83292664e256b978196.avif?t=1778739840\" width=660 height=120 \/><\/span><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/3117820\/extras\/9b69d0a269308a9b4a1edd160cda70f7.poster.avif?t=1778739840\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/3117820\/extras\/9b69d0a269308a9b4a1edd160cda70f7.webm?t=1778739840\" type=\"video\/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/3117820\/extras\/9b69d0a269308a9b4a1edd160cda70f7.mp4?t=1778739840\" type=\"video\/mp4\"><\/video><\/span><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Sultan is not the only horror here. Ancient gods watch from beyond, promising power and salvation. Piece together the cosmic truth across multiple lifetimes. Claim powers no mortal should. Bring down the apocalypse. Kill a god.<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>※ Powered by Live2D<\/i><\/p>","short_description":"Survive a mad Sultan's reign in this brutal resource management RPG. Draw a card every seven days and complete its challenge. Make dreadful choices to stay alive: will you die a loyal servant, become a kingslayer, or call down the gods' judgement?","supported_languages":"English, Simplified Chinese, Japanese, Traditional Chinese","reviews":"“It’s very dark, but it also feels very vibrant with ideas.”<br>Rock Paper Shotgun<br><br>“The result is a dark, challenging, and utterly fascinating puzzle.”<br>PC Gamer<br><br>“The art looks fantastic, and the whole thing is intriguing.”<br>Kotaku<br>","header_image":"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/3117820\/header.jpg?t=1778739840","capsule_image":"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/3117820\/b94